s in continually reinforcing the value proposition we offer to our customers and the commitments weve made to our coworkers the environment and the communities in which we operate by creating highvalue products through innovation we make the world lighter brighter and betterwe work with our customers to incorporate aluminum as the lighter infinitely recyclable material of choice shaping the future of design in transportation packaging electronics and architectural markets around the globeexperience in actionhow does that actually work in realworld applications take the automotive market as an example the future of automobiles is linked to the ability to increase fuel economy reduce emissions and improve safety by reducing vehicle weight through intelligent use of aluminum we deliver on all of those goals thats better for people and its better for the environmentfrom aluminum building structures and architectural facades to aluminum bottles from beverage cans to flatscreen tvs novelis is leading the way in creating products that showcase the light bright and beautiful appearance of our metalbut most importantly novelis is setting the worlds standard for innovation in aluminum products and aluminum recycling we are opening up new applications for existing and new customers and we are doing so by leveraging our technologically sophisticated assets and our unique combination of talent and expertiseour core company valuesthe following values aligned with those of the aditya birla group guide our behavior in support of our strategy as individuals and as a company we live these values every dayintegrityby always striving to act in a manner that is fair and honest we adhere to the highest standards of integrity and professionalism in everything we docommitmentwith integrity as our foundation we are committed to doing whatever it takes to deliver value to all stakeholders by taking responsibility for our own actions and the collective actions of the novelis teampassionwe bring a definitive passion to our relentless pursuit of shared goals and objectives an energetic sense of engagement that is evident in our great enthusiasm for cooperative performanceseamlessnesswe endeavor to think and work seamlessly by leveraging the value of our shared beliefs and best practices across functional business and geographic boundariesspeedby responding to the needs of our customers and partners with focused urgency we continuously seek to accelerate performance and shorten delivery timelines for optimum speed and efficiency our history noveliss company history represents a unique combination of new and old created in  as a spinoff from aluminum producer alcan inc novelis is a young growthoriented company backed by a year history in the aluminum rolling businessour rootsnovelis inherited its core assets manufacturing knowhow and corporate structure from alcan the first alcan rolling operation began in  in toronto ontario with an inch hot mill and three finishing mills most popular related searches heat protection material recycling marine exhaust gas environment health and safety performance container manufacturer exhauster waste to landfill health safety and environment packaging material recycling automotive air featured products automotive heat exchanger bottles  cartridges exhaust pipes beverage cans aluminum container foil heat protection tubes heat protection sleeves and mats flexible tubes for hot  cold air distribution featured services community engagement services environment health safety  quality services raw materials  recycling services events attended rwm in partnership with ciwm  contact supplier contact supplier your message your email your first name your last name i would like to receive periodic email updates and special offers from select suppliers yes please match my request to similar suppliers using xprt sourcing send message cancel and close by continuing you agree to the terms  conditions and privacy policy of this website env