 is its highest earning site the company divides its operations into four regions north america europe asia and south america the regional headquarters are atlanta zurich seoul and sao paulo novelis also has operations in uk germany italy france canada china malaysia and vietnam  demand for aluminum is increasing with the continued development of emerging nations urbanization and the increasing substitution of aluminum for other materials making expansion a key consideration the company invested  million in its first manufacturing facility in china which opened in  in response to global demand for aluminum sheet for automotive electronics and beverage cans the company has announced capital investments including a  million expansion in asia a  million expansion in brazil  and  million expansion in north america in july  it announced that reynolds consumer products inc a subsidiary of the rank group of new zealand purchased the north american consumer products division of novelis for cad mn novelis recycles approximately  billion cans each year productionedit packagingedit foil packaging closures beverage cans  novelis produces sheet aluminum that it sells to the following companies to be made into cans anheuserbusch ball corporation cocacola gz industries ltd nigeria rexam  automotive  transportationedit aluminum structures and components for transportation products in automotive automotive heat exchanger and mass transportation  auto sheet customers include audi bmw ferrari ford gm hyundai mercedesbenz jaguar porsche volvo range rover specialtyedit architecture  building facade roofing insulation shutters lithography  printing consumer goods smartphones laptops tv industrial applications sustainabilityedit in  novelis released its second annual sustainability report the report stated  reduction in energy intensity – halfway to novelis  goal of  percent  reduction in water intensity almost halfway to its goal of  percent  reduction in greenhouse gas emissions representing significant progress towards reaching its total goal of halving novelis absolute ghgs  improvement towards the companys goal of reducing waste to landfill to zero the novelis report received an a rating from the global reporting initiative gri the worlds most widely used framework for sustainability reporting awards and accomplishmentsedit  and  oswego works cash a shift operational excellence  novelis was named metals company of the year and novelis ceo phil martens was named ceo of the year on the platts global metals awards in london   novelis ceo phil martens was named one of the top  ceos in the world by best practice institute   aluminium awards for innovation leadership   american metal market award for aluminum excellence in environmental responsibility in   georgia governor’s international award for establishing its global research  technology center in kennesaw ga  innovation award from bmw  vision award from keep america beautiful notesedit  novelis expanding in brazil atlanta business chronicle retrieved    novelis to invest  million for new coating line in brazil cantech online retrieved    novelis linkedin linkedin retrieved    novelis  our history novelis retrieved    hindalco of india buys aluminum rival new york times retrieved    news and statistics novelis  hindalco’s best growth bet aluminum india retrieved    aditya birla group novelis aditya birla retrieved    novelis president charts sustainable future for rolled aluminum products industry pr newswire retrieved    novelis  geographic locations novelis retrieved    industry statistics reveal increasing domestic demand production and consumption for aluminum the aluminum association retrieved    novelis to build  mn plant in china businessstandard retrieved    novelis to open shanghai office aluminium today retrieved    novelis builds on its footprint atlanta journal constitution retrieved    novelis completes sale of north america consumer foil business to reynolds consumer products novel